(49432, 150478, 4541, 9, 'Voice Over', 'Watch Voice over acoustic radio session: \r\nwww.youtube.com/watch?v=PiBKujYD3AU', '2010-12-01 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 7, 'Life, is an engine \r\nThat’s pushing us all to find if \r\nWho gives his advice: \r\nJust living feels so good \r\n\r\nIt cheers us \r\nI love it \r\nIt cheers us \r\nI hear you \r\n\r\nFind me a scanner \r\nFor tracking my voice \r\nAnd feed it into the silence breaker \r\nForcing the sound \r\nJust hear it, it feels so good \r\n\r\nVoice over \r\n\r\nIt cheers us \r\nI love it \r\nIt cheers us \r\nI hear you', '', 239, '', 'Guy Ben Shetrit', 'Guy Ben Shetrit', 'Eatliz', 'Anova Music', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-06-15 06:20:58', '2015-03-12 13:53:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
